reviewText: Good and what I wanted but the quality is pretty much in need of magical digital repair.

This DVD is a compilation of videos remastered, but not that well. It's presentation is too formal and militaristic and the images are not that good. I give it four stars for it's historical value only.

Bought this DVD for my Dad, & he loved it. He especially liked the manual that is on the DVD as a bonus. As a life long mechanic in the Air Force who started on P-51's, he enjoyed looking at 1 plane he never worked on.
